data.description: Welcome Home to 5509 North Natoma! This Beautiful and Large Home is For You to Appreciate the Uniqueness of a Modern Styled Home. You'll Find 3 Bedrooms, 3.5 Bathrooms with 4th Bedroom or office in a Full Finished Basement! Welcoming Kitchen with SS & Appliances & sliding Glass Doors to a Nice Deck Awaits you. Open Floor Plan Featuring Hardwood Floors and marble fireplace in the living room. Separate Dining Room, and massive Master Suite. Lower level also includes Large Recreation Room and full Bath. Home comes with Commercial Level Fire Alarm System, and Dual entry and Exit 2 Care Garage.
